ctags

From: http://andrew.stwrt.ca/posts/vim-ctags/

#Add tags file in current directory
   • ctags -R .
   • include function prototypes from header files
      ◦ ctags -R -—c-kinds=+p
   • include language flag (needed for easytags)
      ◦ ctags -—fields=+l ——c-kinds=+p -R

#Add tags file in .git folder
This will keep tags file hidden
   • ctags -R -f ./.git/tags .
